<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{pageTitle}}</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">{{pageTitle}}</h1>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <h3>복합 데이터 구조 처리 예제</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>문법 설명</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">중첩된 반복문과 조건문을 조합하여 복잡한 데이터를 처리합니다.</p>

            <h4>통계 정보</h4>
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{totalPosts}}</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">전체 게시글</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{publishedCount}}</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">게시된 글</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h4>게시글 목록</h4>
            {{#posts}}
                <article class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{title}}</h5>
                            <!-- 조건부 배지 -->
                            {{#published}}
                                <span class="badge bg-success">게시됨</span>
                            {{/published}}
                            {{^published}}
                                <span class="badge bg-warning">임시저장</span>
                            {{/published}}
                        </div>

                        <p class="card-text">
                            <small class="text-muted">작성자: {{author}}</small>
                        </p>

                        <!-- 태그 목록 (중첩 반복문) -->
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <strong>태그:</strong>
                            {{#tags}}
                                <span class="badge bg-secondary me-1">#{{.}}</span>
                            {{/tags}}
                            {{^tags}}
                                <span class="text-muted">태그 없음</span>
                            {{/tags}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            {{/posts}}
            {{^posts}}
                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    <p>작성된 게시글이 없습니다.</p>
                </div>
            {{/posts}}

            <div class="mt-4">

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/mustache/nested-objects" class="btn btn-secondary">이전</a>
        <a href="/mustache/basic-variables" class="btn btn-success">처음으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>